      <talk_question mid="31"><![CDATA[<html>$Invisible Thief$<BR>Well, I happen to have free time now, let me tell you about Phantom Thief Shupin's legend. Don't be misunderstood, it's not because I have <FONT color=#a82424>nothing to steal and nothing to do</FONT>!</html>]]></talk_question>
