      <talk_question mid="33"><![CDATA[<html>$Invisible Thief$<BR>Phantom Thief Shupin was such a great person. Not only he helped the poor by stealing things, he was famous for his various <FONT color=#a82424>inventions</FONT>.</html>]]></talk_question>
