      <talk_question mid="40"><![CDATA[<html>$Invisible Thief$<BR>Can you imagine? <FONT color=#a82424>A yellow bird that enables someone far away to hear your voice</FONT>. This cute little birdie makes your voice to be heard from afar! Fascinating isn't it?</html>]]></talk_question>
